Accounts Module
------------------
1. Add KYC Block, which will have KYC Status, and KYC Data.
2. Add Payment Modes, which will have redacted details for payments.
3. Add recommendations, which will contain tags, basics of user purchase history and recommends from Inventory
4. Seller's Account
5. Proper User management, with ACLs

Inventory Module
------------------
1. Single Inventory item can be mapped against multiple sellers
2. Have offers sections, where depending on the payment mode selected, offers to be applied
3. Seller can add items in inventory

Orders Module
------------------
1. Cancellation request to be raised to seller
2. Can order multiple items from inventory
3. Authorizing users, before doing write operations in orders